sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant GM as Global Mic
    participant C as Control plane
    participant X as Master model<br/>(Claude Opus 4.6, 1M ctx)
    participant GC as Global Camera
    participant MC as Mirror Camera
    participant L as Lamp runtime
    participant LA as Lamp agent<br/>(Qwen via Cerebras/Groq)
    participant M as Mirror runtime
    participant MA as Mirror agent<br/>(Qwen via Cerebras/Groq)
    participant Ra as Radio runtime
    participant RaA as Radio agent<br/>(Qwen via Cerebras/Groq)
    participant Rv as Rover runtime
    participant RvA as Rover agent<br/>(Qwen via Cerebras/Groq)

    Note over U,RvA: DETERMINISTIC COMMAND (no model on either side)
    U->>GM: "Lamp blue"
    GM->>GM: VAD + Whisper
    GM->>C: DeviceEvent(kind=transcript)
    C->>C: deterministic route: match
    C-->>L: command: set_color blue
    L->>L: direct command handler (no model)
    L->>L: execute hardware
    L-->>C: action_result

    Note over U,RvA: REASONING PATH (two-tier model)
    U->>GM: "I need to lock in"
    GM->>GM: VAD + Whisper
    GM->>C: DeviceEvent(kind=transcript)
    C->>C: router: no deterministic match
    C->>X: assembled prompt + tools
    X-->>C: tool_use: update_user_state + send_to_lamp + send_to_mirror + send_to_rover
    C->>C: persist state.json

    par Master dispatches NL intents to devices
        C-->>L: spawn: "Focus lighting, show determination — perk up"
        C-->>M: spawn: "Show an encouraging visual about locking in"
        C-->>Rv: spawn: "Head over to the user with their supplies"
    end

    Note over L,LA: Device agent loops (parallel)
    L->>LA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    LA->>LA: plan: set_color(blue, brightness=40)
    LA-->>L: tool calls
    L->>L: execute hardware
    LA->>LA: check: done
    L-->>C: action_result

    M->>MA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    MA->>MA: plan: display_image(encouragement_visual)
    MA-->>M: tool calls
    M->>M: execute hardware
    MA->>MA: check: done
    M-->>C: action_result

    Rv->>RvA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    RvA->>RvA: plan: drive_to(desk)
    RvA-->>Rv: tool calls
    Rv->>Rv: execute hardware
    RvA->>RvA: check: done
    Rv-->>C: action_result

    Note over U,RvA: VISION PATH (global camera or Mirror camera)
    GC->>GC: motion gate + frame capture
    GC->>C: DeviceEvent(kind=frame, source: global_camera)
    C->>C: vision.py: Claude Vision analysis
    C->>C: significant mood change detected
    C->>C: enqueue vision_result event
    C->>X: vision_result + state + recent context
    X-->>C: tool_use: update_user_state + send_to_lamp + send_to_mirror + send_to_radio
    C->>C: persist state.json

    par Master dispatches NL intents
        C-->>L: spawn: "Shift to warm relaxing light, gentle sway"
        C-->>M: spawn: "Suggest taking a break with a gentle visual"
        C-->>Ra: spawn: "Play some calming music"
    end

    L->>LA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    LA-->>L: tool calls
    L->>L: execute hardware
    L-->>C: action_result

    M->>MA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    MA-->>M: tool calls
    M->>M: execute hardware
    M-->>C: action_result

    Ra->>RaA: SOUL.md + HW tools + sensors + instruction
    RaA-->>Ra: tool calls
    Ra->>Ra: execute hardware
    Ra-->>C: action_result
